Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:19.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fnGulim\b0\fsp1\fs27\1a&H22&\bord0\shad0\pos(23,85)}Moje hobby je písať si svoj denník.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:19.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fnGulim\b0\fsp1\fs27\1a&H22&\bord0\shad0\pos(39,51)}Toto nie je nič pre mňa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:34.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGulim\b0\fsp1\1a&H22&\bord0\shad0\pos(320,75)}Nemám nič.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fnGulim\b0\fsp1\fs27\1a&H22&\bord0\shad0\pos(51,85)}Nemám žiadne sny,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fnGulim\b0\fsp1\fs27\1a&H22&\bord0\shad0\pos(168,116)}žiadne ciele.
